        <div class="article_content">
            <p>Earlier this year, IGN headed north to Bellevue, WA  to take our first look at the next game from the creator's of Halo: <a class="autolink" href="http://ps3.ign.com/objects/072/072314.html">Destiny</a>. Today, we can finally tell you all about it.</p>
<p>Join IGN's Casey Lynch and Ryan McCaffrey for the first look at <a class="autolink" href="http://xbox360.ign.com/objects/142/14284232.html">Destiny</a>. <em>A note, this is archived footage and not live.</em></p>
<div class="aligncenter">

    
